  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1037">
<l>toṭippuḻuti kaḵcā vuṇakkiṟ piṭitteruvum</l>
<l>vēṇṭāmaṟ cālap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the land is dried so as to reduce one ounce of earth to a quarter, it will grow plentifully even without a handful of manure.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
